      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion softens, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 350ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[500ml]</span> [650ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p>",
